  "detailed_description": "<h1>Connection Methods</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game supports Steam Remote Play Together, but if you experience severe lag or latency when using Remote Play Together, it is recommended to use third-party software for online play, such as Parsec.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Please refer to the official documentation for instructions on using Steam Remote Play Together.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Parsec Illustrated Tutorial</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/fa2119631a3504a7f020026d5137b1a5.avif?t=1768790513\" width=600 height=2210 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/cfc1d96b1e87a43a8d2a4cf5be4ccbbf.poster.avif?t=1768790513\" width=780 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/cfc1d96b1e87a43a8d2a4cf5be4ccbbf.webm?t=1768790513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/cfc1d96b1e87a43a8d2a4cf5be4ccbbf.mp4?t=1768790513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PS. This game currently only supports two-player local play! But we don’t mind you challenging yourself to control two players at once and unlock all the achievements! We believe this will be a great feat. You can also invite your friends to join the competition using the STEAM Remote Play Together feature.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of toys, where you will be provided with a stage for free battle! Use your fists or randomly dropped weapons to start a crazy melee! The only rule in this \"performance\" is: don't take it too seriously, as happiness is the only goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Do as you please and fight wildly</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/924cbf12d68b1160b4e9115b6546aec1.poster.avif?t=1768790513\" width=700 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/924cbf12d68b1160b4e9115b6546aec1.webm?t=1768790513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/924cbf12d68b1160b4e9115b6546aec1.mp4?t=1768790513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports multiple players battling on the same stage, with no complicated rules or the need for precise calculations. Your only goal is to defeat your opponents or knock them off the stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Diverse maps and varied scenes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/b0dfae5c403b395e5c5f5c78e2190b7a.poster.avif?t=1768790513\" width=700 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/b0dfae5c403b395e5c5f5c78e2190b7a.webm?t=1768790513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/b0dfae5c403b395e5c5f5c78e2190b7a.mp4?t=1768790513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch randomly between a variety of maps, while randomly distributed dangerous traps and unpredictable meteorites pose threats. Please be careful to dodge them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Playful skins, relaxed battles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/8e76203962410e67bf8e88d0ae2f611b.avif?t=1768790513\" width=700 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bananas? Spacesuits? Hot dogs? Hmm...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wide range of quirky skins awaits your discovery, inspired by your daily life or internet memes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiple weapons, one-click use</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/1a7457cff503e2c870cec315295f6a83.poster.avif?t=1768790513\" width=700 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/1a7457cff503e2c870cec315295f6a83.webm?t=1768790513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/1a7457cff503e2c870cec315295f6a83.mp4?t=1768790513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up randomly dropped weapons and fire bullets into the sky! Or, at your opponents~ Various melee and ranged weapons will be randomly scattered across the map, waiting for you to use them.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/cfc1d96b1e87a43a8d2a4cf5be4ccbbf.poster.avif?t=1768790513\" width=780 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/cfc1d96b1e87a43a8d2a4cf5be4ccbbf.webm?t=1768790513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/cfc1d96b1e87a43a8d2a4cf5be4ccbbf.mp4?t=1768790513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PS. This game currently only supports two-player local play! But we don’t mind you challenging yourself to control two players at once and unlock all the achievements! We believe this will be a great feat. You can also invite your friends to join the competition using the STEAM Remote Play Together feature.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of toys, where you will be provided with a stage for free battle! Use your fists or randomly dropped weapons to start a crazy melee! The only rule in this \"performance\" is: don't take it too seriously, as happiness is the only goal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Do as you please and fight wildly</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/924cbf12d68b1160b4e9115b6546aec1.poster.avif?t=1768790513\" width=700 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/924cbf12d68b1160b4e9115b6546aec1.webm?t=1768790513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/924cbf12d68b1160b4e9115b6546aec1.mp4?t=1768790513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports multiple players battling on the same stage, with no complicated rules or the need for precise calculations. Your only goal is to defeat your opponents or knock them off the stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Diverse maps and varied scenes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/b0dfae5c403b395e5c5f5c78e2190b7a.poster.avif?t=1768790513\" width=700 height=392 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/b0dfae5c403b395e5c5f5c78e2190b7a.webm?t=1768790513\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/b0dfae5c403b395e5c5f5c78e2190b7a.mp4?t=1768790513\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch randomly between a variety of maps, while randomly distributed dangerous traps and unpredictable meteorites pose threats. Please be careful to dodge them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Playful skins, relaxed battles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3432130/extras/8e76203962410e67bf8e88d0ae2f611b.avif?t=1768790513\" width=700 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bananas? Spacesuits? Hot dogs? Hmm...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A wide range of quirky skins awaits your discovery, inspired by your daily life or internet memes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiple weapons, one-click use</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\